subject: Update CLAUDE.md to remove outdated "Complete Designs" references
body:
The Presets tab now has three sections: Layout, Themes, and Looks.
"Complete Designs" was replaced by "Looks" which applies overlay, fonts,
and filters without changing layout or colors.
